title: Il Biomarket
description: Comprehensively stocked organic store. Carries many vegan staples: seitan, tofu, soya yoghurt, soya milk, rice milk, oat milk, vegetable pates, ready made vegan savories and vegan desserts, nuts, pulses, beans, dried fruits, wines. Selection of organic fresh produce. Eco-cleaning products with refill service. Home delivery service available.
